##A month, melt-blown cloth increased more than ten times, still can not buy

The papernews

The function introduction, has the connotation the current politics new media

Reporter from the paper, Li Siwen, intern, Xia Mengjie

"meltblown cloth [ prices ] have gone up 10-fold and ear bands [ prices ] have gone up more than five-fold. "

The company is under pressure to double its costs while producing at full capacity, the head of a medical and health products company in Zhejiang told The Paper recently. Among them, melt-blown cloth as the core material of mask filter bacteria, in just a month price from 20,000 / ton, jumped to 200-300,000 / ton.

According to interviews with a number of relevant enterprises by thepaper.cn, meltblown cloth enterprises and special meltblown cloth enterprises are facing problems such as a shortage of production lines, high production requirements and long equipment procurement cycle, and their production capacity is far from meeting the market demand, causes the supply and demand imbalance, some mask factory has the machine, has the worker, but lacks melts spurts the cloth, and under "the sky-high price" still "a cloth is difficult to obtain" .

The person in charge of the meltblown cloth production enterprise reminds that under the interest drive, the meltblown cloth that does not have the effect of isolating bacteria also begins to mix more and more into the market, or will lead to the spread of "fake medical masks" that do not have the effect of isolating viruses.

STATUS: The price of melt-blown cloth has increased to 10 times, enterprises are under pressure

Meng Heping's company, a private enterprise in Sichuan Province, started to produce medical masks on Feb. 3, when the price of meltblown fabric had already risen. On February 8, he bought 40,000 per ton, he said, and 10 days later the price rose. He bought a ton of material for 180,000 yuan through the local government, he said. On the 27th, he was told that the MELTZER cloth was already selling for 250,000 per ton. Years ago, a tonne of Meltzer cloth cost just 20,000 yuan. In just 30 days, the price of a ton of meltblown cloth has risen more than ten-fold.

But all the way up the price of meltblown cloth, is all the production of medical masks companies are around the ridge.

"The medical mask has three layers, and the melt-blown cloth is the middle layer. It has strong filterability, shielding and heat insulation. It can kill bacteria and isolate viruses. It can be said to be the 'heart' of a medical mask, " Meng said, "A tonne of meltblown cloth can produce six hundred thousand medical masks, and we have only 10-20 days of material available. "

Meng Pinghe said that his company produced medical masks at its own expense and distributed them free to local residents, and that the "sky-high" price of meltblown cloth had put him in a dilemma, "We are also looking everywhere for meltblown cloth. A few days ago, someone said that another place has the goods, 250,000 a ton to want or not to want, I said no, it is really too expensive. "

Zhejiang Jinhua Jiurui mask factory, which specializes in the production of face masks, sensed the rising price of melt-blown cloth earlier than Meng Pinghe, general Manager Ye Zhenhao said: "since the New Year has begun to rise, before the general is 20,000 a ton, before the beginning of the year all the way up, now some of the highest has sold more than 300,000. "

After the rise in raw materials, it became more and more difficult for Ye Zhenhao's mask factory to survive, "under the epidemic situation, it was already very difficult to buy meltblown cloth, but now it's so much more expensive that the cost has to go up. If the manufacturers want to not lose money, they have to raise the price of medical masks. But now the state has limited the price of medical masks. We can't make money, and we may lose money. The domestic market is now very difficult to do, and doing foreign trade is better. "

Since the beginning of production of medical masks on January 27, Zhejiang Ampson Medical Equipment Co. , Ltd. (hereinafter referred to as ampson medical) has faced a shortage of melt-blown cloth, contact local media in Zhejiang for urgent sourcing of raw materials. Now, more than a month after starting work, ampson medical is still facing the problem of meltblown cloth.

"Now the meltblown cloth has increased more than 10 times, and if you want to buy it, you can't buy it, " said Jiang Jiang, the company's general manager, in the past, he was in the enterprise from Hangzhou, Hunan, Jiangsu and other different manufacturers purchase, during the Spring Festival, because the factory did not resume work, once a shortage of raw materials, then slowly recover. But more than 10 days ago, the melt-blown cloth on the market again appeared "a cloth hard to get" situation.

"At present, such fabrics as meltblown fabrics are guaranteed to be used locally, so it is difficult for us to buy them outside of China, " Jiang said. At present, meltblown fabrics used in the factory are bought by acquaintances, but there is only a small supply.

Jiang also believes that a large number of enterprises into the medical mask market, also let the price of meltblown cloth rising ship high. "Now, in addition to the mask factories expanding their production lines, many companies are turning to medical masks, especially the big ones. They have sufficient funds and can stockpile a large amount of meltblown cloth at a time, which makes it even more difficult for our small professional manufacturers to get supplies. "

In addition to the price increase of the meltblown cloth, other mask raw materials are also facing the problem of price increase. Jiang told The Paper that the ear straps (elastic straps) used in the mask are the second largest price increase among raw materials, and have already increased more than fivefold, although there is no purchase difficulties, but the price of raw materials, to the enterprise has brought a lot of pressure.

"In the past, it cost only a few cents to produce a common medical mask. Now, with the price of raw materials rising, the cost has doubled to more than 1 yuan, but the government has set a maximum purchase price, and our enterprises are in difficulty, " Jiang said.

Traceability: MELTBLOWN cloth production capacity is low, enterprises said that the main middleman in the price increase

Melt-blown Cloth Price Meng Zhang, raw material production enterprise status?

Hunan Shengjin New Material Co. , Ltd. is a leading manufacturer of special materials for meltblown cloth, "We produce meltblown cloth particles, which are polypropylene particles, that melt and spray onto the cloth in a process that acts as a barrier, " Tian Boling, a director of the company, told The Paper, since January 28, the company fully resumed work, and maintain full load production, still can not meet the needs of special materials for meltblown cloth.

"Now all orders have been filled, and all other orders will not be filled until March 15. Now we can only meet the old customers, but we can no longer take orders from new customers, " Tian said, now companies receive orders are mainly in accordance with the Ministry of Industry and Information Technology Guarantee List, provided to the list of pillar-sized enterprises, many small enterprises can not take into account.

In the chain of medical mask, meltblown cloth, meltblown cloth special material, raw material, special material is the most important link.

Tianboling said that the production of special materials for meltblown cloth is the main raw material for Polypropylene (PP) , material supply mainly from Sinopec. According to public reports, on February 18, Sinopec and CNPC both urgently adjusted their production facilities to produce medical polyolefins to meet the demand of medical materials such as special materials for non-woven polypropylene fiber and medical polypropylene.

From polypropylene to meltblown cloth, where is the card?

"The main reason is limited production capacity and High Acceptance Standard, " said Tian Boling. At present, there are many domestic non-woven fabric factories, but due to the low profit and high technical requirements of the special materials for meltblown fabrics, which belong to the niche field, the manufacturers are very few, "There are basically only a few big companies that can survive. "

Tianboling said that at present, a special material production line can produce 10-15 tons of special materials a day, assuming there are 50 production lines, a day can only supply 500-600 tons. "Now everyone is on a large number of mask machine, think a mask machine can solve the problem, but after the finished found a lack of meltblown cloth, meltblown cloth production line and found that there is no special material, in fact, this is one ring after another. "

However, Tian Bolingcheng, under the soaring demand and the soaring price of melt-blown cloth, the profit of the special material for melt-blown cloth has not changed too much, "The companies that produce meltblown cloth ask us to buy special materials only 10,000 / tons, after production meltblown cloth sells more than 200,000 / tons, even 400,000 / tons on the black market. " Although the upstream determines the output, the profits are basically in the downstream.

And in the special material downstream, meltblown cloth production enterprises also have pressure.

In response to the rising prices of meltblown fabrics by the largest meltblown fabric manufacturer in Xiantao, the head of the company, the Communist Party of China (Zhonghua) , said it was more middlemen selling the products, "Now the prices of Meltfoam are very chaotic, our ex-factory prices are actually not high, mainly middlemen selling in the middle of the markup, " he told The Paper news, the current profit is only a small increase over the past, but there are more problems.

Party China told The Paper that it now has only one production line, and that it can produce about 2.5 million disposable surgical masks a day from meltblown fabric, but that it is still woefully inadequate, "even if we increase our production capacity by 10 times, " he said.

As one of the key manufacturing enterprises of materials for epidemic prevention and control in Xiantao, the meltblown fabric production needs to mainly ensure the supply of meltblown fabric in Hubei, "We have now completely repented the contracts of our customers elsewhere, all of whom want the goods, but we can not even guarantee our local enterprises in Hubei, " said party Zhonghua, who used to run the production lines for only eight hours a day, now it's 24 hours a day, and demand is still outstripping supply.

The party has also considered adding production lines, but the equipment production cycle is so long that it would take at least eight months to add one.

What worries the Party and China most is the problem of the source of tourists, "Now, in order to ensure the supply of Hubei, we have all turned down the foreign enterprises and stopped the supply. The foreign customers have to find other manufacturers to cooperate. This means that after the epidemic has passed, we may face the problem of large-scale loss of customers, which is related to the survival of our enterprises, " he said, i don't know if my business will be able to produce after the outbreak.

CAUTION: to guard against non-standard meltblown cloth, enterprises proposed to strengthen supervision

Demand surge, price increases, melt-blown cloth quality problems are also facing the test.

"We can only say that fakes are coming in every year, but this year there are a lot of fakes, " Jiang Jiang, general manager of Ampson Medical, told The Paper news. Inferior meltblown fabrics have always been on the market. He said that previous mask manufacturers and most familiar with the meltblown cloth manufacturers, now in demand surge, some of the meltblown cloth manufacturers by local supervision, mask factories have to look for new sources, inferior meltblown cloth or overflow.

Jiang Jiang said that the true "fake" melt-blown cloth is more difficult to identify, and needs professional testing. Testing costs are high, but it is easier to produce low-quality melt-blown cloth, "meltblown cloth all need to achieve a certain filtering effect and index, fake meltblown cloth will not reach the standard, that is, it will not play the role of virus protection, and some fake even static adsorption is not up to the standard, there is no isolation of the virus effect. "

Tian boling analyzed the special material of meltblown cloth. He told The Paper that both the outer and inner layers of the mask are only supporting functions. The most important thing for filtering the virus is the middle meltblown cloth, which has a filtering efficiency of 50% and needs to be processed to increase electrostatic adsorption, to achieve more than 99% bacterial filtration (BFE99 for short) .

"A 50 percent filter-effective meltblown cloth can only be used as a protective mask for civil use. It can only prevent dust and dust, and can not isolate viruses, but all medical masks and surgical masks must be used with a 99 percent filter-effective meltblown cloth, " Tian said, production filter 99% melt-blown cloth takes a long time, will reduce production capacity, in the interest-driven, someone May "fake" , "It means that they will produce sub-standard meltblown cloth and make it into a mask that is clearly a civil protective mask and has no protection against viruses, instead of being 99% of medical masks. "

On February 26, the State Council held a press conference on the joint prevention and control mechanism for the COVID-19 infection of pneumonia. The Ministry of Public Security said that 688 cases of manufacturing and selling fake and inferior masks and other protective materials have been detected, and more than 1,560 criminal suspects have been arrested, more than 31 million counterfeit masks and a batch of protective materials were seized, involving a value of 174 million yuan. Of these, 70 percent are sold through wechat friend circles and wechat commerce.

As a manufacturer of meltblown fabrics, party China told The Paper news that he has learned that there are more fake and inferior meltblown fabrics on the market at present, and hopes that the relevant departments can strengthen control, while strictly checking fake and substandard, three-free medical masks, should also strengthen the supervision of meltblown cloth products. "It is very difficult for ordinary people to distinguish the quality of the meltblown cloth in a medical mask. If you buy a medical mask that has no protective effect, the harm will be greater. "
